easyphp apache config :

## Virtualhost localweb

Listen 127.0.0.1:80

<VirtualHost 127.0.0.1>
	DocumentRoot "G:/WinApp/EasyPHP-Devserver-17/eds-www"
	ServerName 127.0.0.1
	<Directory "G:/WinApp/EasyPHP-Devserver-17/eds-www">
		Options FollowSymLinks Indexes ExecCGI
		AllowOverride All
		Order allow,deny
		Allow all
		Require all granted
	</Directory>
</VirtualHost>



## Virtualhost externe

Listen [your ip]:8080

<VirtualHost [your ip]>
	DocumentRoot "[your directory]"
	ServerName 127.0.0.1
	<Directory "[your directory]">
		Options FollowSymLinks Indexes ExecCGI
		AllowOverride All
		Allow from all
		Require all granted
	</Directory>
</VirtualHost>


